== apps/api/src/auth.test.ts test names ==
- exposes health without authentication and includes a request id
- logs in a seeded user without exposing the token in logs
- rejects empty credentials with a canonical error
- rejects missing, malformed, and unknown bearer tokens
- returns session and bounded authorized projects for a valid token
- selects an authorized project and rejects a forbidden project
== apps/api/src/chat.test.ts test names ==
- requires auth and a matching selected project before reading chat
- stores and returns chat messages only for the selected project
- rejects chat writes without selected project, write permission, or valid body
- rechecks membership on every operation and isolates projects between users
== apps/web/src/App.test.tsx test names ==
- logs in, selects a project, loads chat, and sends project-scoped messages
- guards the workspace when unauthenticated and clears invalid stored tokens
- displays forbidden API errors with request ids without mutating the selected project
- keeps current chat state on chat failure and shows the backend diagnostic
- validates empty login fields, blank chat messages, malformed JSON, and local API outages
- surfaces malformed API JSON as api_malformed without crashing
- renders read-only selected projects without usable chat compose controls
